Package: pve-microvm
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         pve-qemu-kvm (>= 9.0),
         qemu-server (>= 9.0),
         skopeo,
         umoci,
         qemu-utils
Recommends: pve-manager
Description: QEMU microvm machine type support for Proxmox VE
 Adds the QEMU microvm machine type as a managed guest type in Proxmox VE.
 Provides patches to qemu-server for microvm-aware command generation,
 a helper tool to convert OCI container images into bootable microvm disk
 images, and a minimal microvm kernel configuration.
 .
 microvm guests boot in under 200ms, use virtio-mmio devices instead of
 PCI, and provide full KVM hardware isolation with minimal attack surface.
